---
title: Sausage and Pepper Pomodoro Skillet with Melty Mozz and Italian Cheese
description: No matter the weather, it’s pretty much impossible not to daydream about cheesy baked carbs. This killer skillet is guaranteed to make those dreams a reality. In it, you’ll find slices of Italian sausage, roasted bell pepper, and fluffy rice all enrobed in a rich marinara sauce. To top things off, there’s a melty layer of mozzarella and Italian cheese. Serve it right from the pan for maximum cheese pull potential and wait for the oohs and aahs from your lucky fellow diners.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sausage-and-pepper-pomodoro-skillet-bfc32ce2.jpg
